.TP
.PD 0
.B "\-W help"
.TP
.PD 0
.B "\-W usage"
.TP
.PD 0
.B \-\^\-help
.TP
.PD
.B \-\^\-usage
Print a relatively short summary of the available options on
the standard output.
(Per the
.IR "GNU Coding Standards" ,
these options cause an immediate, successful exit.)
.TP
.PD 0
.B "\-W lint"
.TP
