.B \-\^\-lint
Provide warnings about constructs that are
dubious or non-portable to other \*(AK implementations.
.TP
.PD 0
.B "\-W lint\-old"
.TP
.PD
.B \-\^\-lint\-old
Provide warnings about constructs that are
not portable to the original version of Unix
.IR awk .
.ig
.\" This option is left undocumented, on purpose.
.TP
